Name: Average time from 'Accepted + Assigned' to 'Completed + In Call'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Assigned' and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Average resolution time of 'Accepted + Assigned' cases
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Assigned' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Total time for 'Accepted + Assigned' to transition to 'Accepted + In Progress'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Assigned' and activity 'Accepted + In Progress'

Name: Minimum time from 'Accepted + Assigned' to 'Completed + Resolved'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Assigned' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Average time it takes 'Accepted + Assigned' to be followed by 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Assigned' and activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment'

Name: Total resolution time of cases starting with 'Accepted + Assigned' and ending with 'Completed + Closed'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Assigned' and activity 'Completed + Closed'

Name: Minimum time it takes from 'Accepted + Assigned' to 'Accepted + Wait - User'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Assigned' and activity 'Accepted + Wait - User'

Name: Average time for 'Accepted + Assigned' before transitioning to any 'Completed' status
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Assigned' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Total time for 'Accepted + Assigned' activities across all cases
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Accepted + Assigned and the end of the case

Name: Average time from 'Accepted + Assigned' to 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' considering all variants
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Assigned' and activity 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation'

Name: Minimum resolution time of 'Accepted + Assigned' in cases with 'High' impact
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Assigned' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Average time from 'Accepted + Assigned' to 'Completed + In Call' in cases ending with 'Completed + Closed'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Assigned' and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Assigned' and activity 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor'

Name: Minimum time for 'Accepted + Assigned' to transition to 'Completed + Resolved' in cases with 'Medium' impact
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Assigned' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Average time it takes for 'Accepted + Assigned' to be followed by 'Accepted + Wait - Customer' in the log
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Assigned' and activity 'Accepted + Wait - Customer'

Name: Average time for 'Accepted + Assigned' before it leads to any 'Accepted' status in subsequent activities
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Assigned' and activity 'Accepted + In Progress'

Name: Minimum time it takes 'Accepted + Assigned' to transition to 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' in the least frequent process variant
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Assigned' and activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment'
